data.title: Live Jazz Night
data.description: Join us for an evening of smooth jazz with local artists. Enjoy craft cocktails and good vibes in our lounge.

data.title: Cannabis Education Workshop
data.description: Learn about different strains, consumption methods, and responsible use. Expert-led workshop with Q&A session.

data.title: Comedy Open Mic
data.description: Laugh the night away with SF's funniest up-and-coming comedians. Free entry, 21+ only.

data.title: Yoga & Meditation Session
data.description: Start your day with mindfulness. Beginner-friendly yoga and guided meditation. Mats provided.

data.title: Trivia Night
data.description: Test your knowledge! Teams of up to 6. Prizes for top 3 teams. Topics include pop culture, history, and cannabis facts.

data.title: DJ Night: House & Techno
data.description: Dance the night away with DJ Elektra spinning house and techno. Full bar available.

data.title: Paint & Puff
data.description: Unleash your creativity! All art supplies included. No experience necessary. Take home your masterpiece.

data.title: Sunday Brunch & Beats
data.description: Relax with brunch specials and chill beats from our resident DJ. Limited seating, reserve ahead.

data.title: Product Launch: New Strains
data.description: Be the first to try our latest premium strains. Special launch pricing and free samples for attendees.

data.title: Acoustic Lounge
data.description: Intimate acoustic performances featuring local singer-songwriters. Cozy atmosphere, craft drinks.

data.title: Game Night: Board Games & Chill
data.description: Bring your friends for board games and card games. We provide the games, you bring the fun!

data.title: Cannabis & Cuisine Pairing
data.description: Explore flavor profiles with our sommelier. Learn how to pair cannabis strains with gourmet dishes. Limited seats.
